            <p>1941-Tries to enroll in the military after Pearl Harbor attack,but is rejecte. Instead the military has his lab to work on waterproof glue,DDT to control malaria, disinfectants and other applied Service</p>
            <p>1942-Receives Ph.D in Genetics and plants Pathology</p>
